data.description: Come cozy up in this updated Creekside Rancher only 5 minutes from town, with every out building you could need! Interiors charm with beautiful hardwood floors, renovated bathrooms, a large non-conforming primary bedroom and open concept living spaces. Large, central pellet stove, additional electric wall heat & partially updated windows. Exteriors boast a huge deck overlooking the year around Gold Creek. Great barn with stables, corral & hay storage. Additional large pole building for auto storage AND detached one car garage! Perimeter fencing for your animals, acres of sloped trails & trees to explore & a protected garden. Circle drive off county maintained paved road. Come make this your Homestead Close to Town!
